-- Li Ka-shing Said to Buy EDF's U.K. Power Unit for $9.1 Billion
-- Dirk Beveridge
-- 2010-07-30T04:58:23Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-30/li-ka-shing-companies-bid-9-billion-for-edf-s-u-k-electricity-networks.html

          
          
             Billionaire Li Ka-shing’s Cheung
Kong Infrastructure Holdings Ltd. and Hongkong Electric Holdings
Ltd. are bidding 5.8 billion pounds for Electricite de France
SA’s U.K. power networks unit, according to a statement to the
Hong Kong stock exchange today.  
          
          


  


        